Not every person is going to be able to understand your code and that is true but complexity and simplicity

02:59.250 --> 03:02.410
is on a spectrum not binary.

03:02.430 --> 03:06.040
It's not either simplistic or complex.

03:06.150 --> 03:08.100
That means it's not right or wrong.

03:08.250 --> 03:09.440
Black and white.

03:09.630 --> 03:17.160
It's all about trying to minimize the complexity of your code as much as you can remember although we

03:17.160 --> 03:19.310
write code to speak with machines.

03:19.530 --> 03:24.690
Machines that work to communicate and make our lives easier.

