So next time you write code take a deep breath say to yourself what can I do to make this code simple

03:32.550 --> 03:37.390
for anyone to understand while still maintaining my goal.

03:37.440 --> 03:38.940
I don't need to show off.

03:38.950 --> 03:41.620
I am aware of what I know and what I can do.

03:41.670 --> 03:51.380
Let me write code that is easy to understand for people to understand to always choose simplicity over

03:51.380 --> 03:52.040
